'''Corporal Burnett''' came to inform the doctors that a sandstorm was forcing them to evacuate.

==History==
When a sandstorm started in Iraq, Burnett came to tell [[Dan Mooney]] that they had to evacuate the area.

==Career==
He is in the US Army.
